2026-05-11T05:31:20.6785993Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6786694Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6787207Z 20    -->
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6787814Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
