2026-05-11T05:31:20.6789932Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6790637Z 22    <!--
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6791170Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6791862Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6792504Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6793280Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6794043Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6794796Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6795557Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6796367Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6797132Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6797866Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6798419Z 33    -->
2026-05-11T05:31:20.6799166Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
